            <title>Vibe Check 0.1.7</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <p>Vibe Check 0.1.7 adjusts deployment notifications for notched and non-notched screens.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Detects notched displays using safe-area and auxiliary menu bar geometry.</li>
                    <li>Positions deployment-ready notifications closer to the notch on notched screens.</li>
                    <li>Uses a more standard top offset on non-notched screens.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
